{"tid":560852,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"201802 小丑神崇拜月","createTime":"2018-02-14T12:58:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T01:55:29.000Z","uid":75655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4450d8dbb04b30b5a004ba79d45313197fe7b56f","tid":560852,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T12:58:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/193946_e18dd5337a9d7ffb8d0f32e297f027b7.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F193946_e18dd5337a9d7ffb8d0f32e297f027b7.jpeg&h=a214b8b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我們在連登的神，<br />\n<br />\n願人都尊神的名為膠；<br />\n<br />\n願神的國降臨；<br />\n<br />\n願神的旨意行在地上，<br />\n<br />\n如同行在連登。<br />\n<br />\n我們日用的膠幣，<br />\n<br />\n求神今日賜給我們。<br />\n<br />\n又求饒恕我們的假膠，<br />\n<br />\n因為我們饒恕假膠的人。<br />\n<br />\n不叫我們遇見試探，<br />\n<br />\n拯救我們脫離耶教。<br />\n<br />\n因為國度、權柄、榮耀、<br />\n<br />\n全是神的，直到永遠。膠們。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown_combo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n會歌：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QdpW6P3tB98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQdpW6P3tB98&d=VEFjepRhu2uQ7%2BsiH2RY6TQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=a5f3f2f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QdpW6P3tB98</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a0aa626e58cf56a5e7952752a326cdb1b8fee2d1","tid":560852,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T12:59:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3acd870c1e39e37b9374335c0ae4213b3b8edeb","tid":560852,"uid":127347,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T13:01:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\